\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 You're not just copying AI output. That's amateur hour and clients can spot it immediately. Instead:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Intake and research
\f0\b0 : Understand what the client needs. Their tone, audience, goals, keywords.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Strategic prompting
\f0\b0 : Use AI to generate outlines, research data, explore angles.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Human editing
\f0\b0 : Restructure, add personality, verify facts, inject genuine insight.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Optimization
\f0\b0 : Format for web, add proper headers, ensure readability.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The AI does the heavy lifting on the blank page problem and research. You provide strategy, judgment, and voice\'97things AI genuinely can't replicate yet.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

