\f1\b Title: Product Descriptions: The Unglamorous $4,000/Month Nobody Talks About
\f0\b0 \
Everyone wants to build the next great app or launch a viral course. Meanwhile, there's an entire industry of e-commerce businesses drowning in blank product pages, desperate for someone\'97anyone\'97who can write descriptions that don't sound like they were translated from Chinese by a drunk robot.\
One of the easiest AI side hustles is writing product descriptions using artificial intelligence. Every online store, from small businesses to e-commerce giants, needs compelling product descriptions to sell their items effectively.\
This is the least sexy, most profitable AI side hustle you can start today.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 Why This Exists\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 E-commerce exploded during the pandemic and never slowed down. Shopify stores, Amazon sellers, Etsy shops\'97they're all launching products faster than they can describe them. Many just copy manufacturer descriptions or leave pages nearly blank.\
Bad product descriptions kill sales. A good one can boost conversion rates by 30% or more. Business owners know this. They just don't have time to write 200 descriptions for their inventory.\
Enter you, armed with AI and a basic understanding of persuasive writing.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 The Actual Work\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 You're not writing novels. Product descriptions are typically:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 50-150 words for standard products\
\ls8\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 200-300 words for higher-ticket items\
\ls8\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Focused on benefits, not just features\
\ls8\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Optimized for search engines\
\ls8\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Written in the brand's voice\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 With AI, you can crank these out in 5-10 minutes each instead of 30-45 minutes. Imagine being able to charge $50 to $75 per hour for a task that takes you only a fraction of that time to complete.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

