\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 The Bigger Point\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The economy is shifting power away from traditional employment and toward people who can deliver specific value efficiently. AI is the lever that makes this possible for regular people, not just those with elite skills or massive capital.\
You don't need to build a unicorn startup. You don't need to become an influencer. You just need to identify what businesses need, deliver it better/faster/cheaper than alternatives, and keep the margin.\
That's not revolutionary advice. It's boring, practical economics. But boring and practical pays the bills while everyone else is waiting for their big break.\
Product descriptions won't change the world. They'll just change your bank account.\
