\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 What This Really Represents\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 This is about leverage. You're using AI to deliver services that previously required hiring a full-time marketing person ($40-60K/year) for a fraction of the cost.\
The business saves money. You make more per hour than traditional employment. AI captures the efficiency gain in the middle.\
That's not exploitative\'97that's how technology should work. The productivity improvement benefits the person doing the work, not just the corporation employing them.\
Social media management won't make you a millionaire. But it will make you $4-6K/month within 90 days if you're consistent and professional.\
And unlike a traditional job, when you get more efficient through better systems and AI tools, you keep the time savings. You don't get assigned more work for the same pay.\
You're not building a revolutionary business. You're building a sustainable income stream that gives you control over your time.\
That's the entire point.\
