\f1\b Title: Email Marketing Services: The Recurring Revenue Nobody Wants to Do
\f0\b0 \
Everyone knows email marketing works. Open rates, click rates, conversion tracking\'97businesses understand the metrics matter. But here's what they actually do: send sporadic emails with terrible subject lines, inconsistent formatting, and zero strategy.\
Why? Because email marketing is tedious, time-consuming, and requires consistency most business owners can't maintain while running their actual business.\
Email marketing remains one of the most effective ways for businesses to communicate with their customers. Many businesses struggle to consistently create engaging emails that drive sales and maintain customer relationships.\
This creates a perfect monetization opportunity for someone with AI tools and basic copywriting knowledge.\
