\f1\b Title: Print-on-Demand with AI Art: The $2,000/Month You Build Once
\f0\b0 \
You don't need to be an artist to sell art anymore. You don't need inventory, shipping logistics, or upfront capital. You just need AI tools that generate images and platforms that handle everything else.\
AI image generators (Midjourney, DALL\'b7E 3, Leonardo, Canva AI) can create unique illustrations or patterns by simply describing them. Turn those creations into products: upload to Redbubble, Etsy, or Gumroad and sell t-shirts, posters, stickers, or phone cases.\
This is genuinely passive income if you set it up correctly. Create designs once, list them on print-on-demand platforms, and earn royalties every time someone buys.\
