\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 What This Actually Represents\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Prompt engineering is a temporary skill that's valuable because AI tools are still clunky and most people don't know how to use them effectively.\
This won't be a $100K/year career in five years. AI will get better at understanding human intent. Prompt engineering will become as common as using Google search.\
But right now? It's a legitimate opportunity to monetize knowledge that most people don't have.\
You're not building a unicorn startup. You're capitalizing on a transitional moment in technology adoption.\
Get in early, build income streams, and prepare for the next opportunity when this one normalizes.\
That's how you navigate a changing economy\'97you spot transitions, monetize them, and move on.\
No romance. Just pragmatic economics.\
