\f1\b Day 4-5
\f0\b0 : Create your first video. Use free tools initially (Canva for visuals, CapCut for editing, free stock footage).\

\f1\b Day 6
\f0\b0 : Design 3 thumbnail options in Canva. Ask friends or post in forums which is most click-worthy.\

\f1\b Day 7
\f0\b0 : Upload first video with optimized title, description, tags, and thumbnail. Start working on video #2.\

\f1\b Ongoing
\f0\b0 : Commit to 2 videos per week minimum for 3 months. Don't evaluate results before hitting that milestone.\
