\cf0 You're building a content library that generates ad revenue and affiliate income perpetually. Videos you create in 2025 can still earn money in 2028.\
This isn't passive income initially\'97it requires consistent content creation for 6-12 months. But once you hit critical mass (1,000+ subscribers, consistent views), the compounding effect kicks in.\
Old videos continue generating views. New videos reach existing subscribers. Total watch time grows. Revenue scales non-linearly.\
This won't make you rich in 90 days. But it will create a legitimate $2,000-4,000/month income stream within a year if you're consistent and strategic.\
That's not hype\'97that's just math and platform mechanics.\
The people who fail quit at month 3 when they have 300 subscribers and no money. The people who succeed push through to month 8 when they have 5,000 subscribers and $1,000/month coming in.\
The difference is patience and consistency, not talent.\
